{
  "text": "The limit in (1.3) must be understood in the distributional sense; see [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] or section 2 for more details. As noted in [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] , the fractional Laplacian and the Dirichlet to Neumann operator of problem (1.2) are related by",
